workflow_1.steps:
{{List each step in the workflow:
1. User action or trigger 2. System response 3. UI changes 4. Validation or processing 5. Success/error handling 6. Next state or screen
Example for "Create New Post": 1. User clicks "New Post" button 2. Modal opens with empty form 3. User enters title, content, selects category 4. User clicks "Save Draft" or "Publish" 5. Client validates required fields 6. Form data sent to POST /api/posts 7. Loading spinner shows on button 8. Server validates and creates post in database 9. On success: Modal closes, success toast, redirect to post 10. On error: Error message shown below relevant field }}

