success_criteria.user_experience:
{{Define UX success criteria:
- Interface is intuitive without training - Navigation is clear and consistent - Feedback is immediate for all actions - Loading states prevent confusion - Error recovery is smooth - Mobile experience is seamless - Animations are smooth (60fps) - First contentful paint < 1.5s
Focus on observable user experience qualities. }}

success_criteria.technical_quality:
{{Define technical standards:
